72
73#define DST_RESULT_RESULTSET 2
74
75static isc_once_t once = ISC_ONCE_INIT;
76
77static void
78initialize_action(void) {
79 isc_result_t result;
80
81 result = isc_result_register(ISC_RESULTCLASS_DST, DST_R_NRESULTS,
82 text, DST_RESULT_RESULTSET);
83 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
84 UNEXPECTED_ERROR(__FILE__, __LINE__,
85 "isc_result_register() failed: %u", result);
86 result = isc_result_registerids(ISC_RESULTCLASS_DST, DST_R_NRESULTS,
87 ids, DST_RESULT_RESULTSET);
88 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
89 UNEXPECTED_ERROR(__FILE__, __LINE__,
90 "isc_result_registerids() failed: %u", result);
91}
92
93static void
94initialize(void) {
95 RUNTIME_CHECK(isc_once_do(&once, initialize_action) == ISC_R_SUCCESS);
96}
97
98const char *
99dst_result_totext(isc_result_t result) {
100 initialize();
101
102 return (isc_result_totext(result));
103}
104
105void
106dst_result_register(void) {
107 initialize();
108}
